#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/04_The_Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:200
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"So this is the Bay of Pearls. It looks like they have those merfolk working "
"hard!"
msgstr "此即珍珠湾，人鱼在此做苦工。"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/04_The_Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:204
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Indeed it does. It also looks like they have many, many troops. I should go "
"around the bay and distract some of them. You and the rest rescue the "
"merfolk!"
msgstr "的确。敌军军势浩大。吾将诱其分散精力。汝等去救人鱼！"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/04_The_Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:208
msgid "Very well. Be careful!"
msgstr "甚好。先生请小心慎事！"

