"...but one of the orcs survived long enough to send the news to the queen..."
msgstr "......然却有一兽人，重伤不死，传信与妖后......"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/08_The_Princess_of_Wesnoth.cfg:50
